- your version asks: Ã¢â‚¬Å“Did `Find` fail right now?Ã¢â‚¬Â
- the current version asks: Ã¢â‚¬Å“After everything we tried, is the reference still missing?Ã¢â‚¬Â

That second idea is often nicer in setup code.

